questions.quote: Nothing, nothing. I'm just taking an interest in what you...do.
Hey, why don't you take her to that place in Vermont I was telling you about? You know, that really charming place with the separate faucets for the hot and cold. She'll love it.
All right, all right, one more time, one more time! What was the exact phrasing of the request?
Guys, there's no doubt that the pay is good. But I don't just know if I see myself working with ice cream.
Do you realize in the entire history of western civilization no one has successfully accomplished the Roommate Switch? In the Middle Ages you could get locked up for even suggesting it!
Why doesn't *he* pick you up after the operation. He's got the car with the bench seats that you like.
How long have you been waiting to squeeze that into a conversation?
You know I'm a little hungry. You wouldn't happen to have any of that mango left?
What's the matter with you? I just wanted to see how tall she was.
What am I gonna do with all these sandwiches?! Will you take them home? Give them to someone in your building?
